            <h3>Tokens (Billing Unit)</h3>
            <p>
              Tokens are like <strong>phone minutes</strong> or <strong>text message characters</strong> ‚Äî you pay for how much you say and how much AI replies.
            </p>
            <div class="token-visual">
              <div class="token-example">
                <span class="token-label">You say one sentence:</span>
                <span class="token-value">‚âà 20 tokens</span>
              </div>
              <div class="token-example">
