            </div>
            <div class="model-cost">
              <strong>üíµ 1 hour daily:</strong> ~$1.50/day
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cost Scenarios -->
      <section class="article-section">
        <h2>üí∏ How Much Will I Spend Daily?</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Don't worry, it's cheaper than you think! Here are real-world scenarios:</p>

        <div class="scenarios-grid">
